                        <para>
                                <figure id="eayunos-install-eayunos-manager-3"><title>图4</title>
                                        <mediaobject>
                                                <imageobject>
                                                        <imagedata fileref="images/eayunos-manager-4.png" format="PNG" scale="100"/>
                                                </imageobject>
                                        </mediaobject>
                                </figure>
                        </para>
                        <para>图中，系统进入格式化中，等待</para>
                        <para>
                                <figure id="eayunos-install-eayunos-manager-4"><title>图5</title>
                                        <mediaobject>
                                                <imageobject>
                                                        <imagedata fileref="images/eayunos-manager-5.png" format="PNG" scale="100"/>
                                                </imageobject>
                                        </mediaobject>
                                </figure>
                        </para>
                        <para>开始安装操作系统</para>
                        <para>
                                <figure id="eayunos-install-eayunos-manager-5"><title>图6</title>
                                        <mediaobject>
                                                <imageobject>
                                                        <imagedata fileref="images/eayunos-manager-6.png" format="PNG" scale="100"/>
                                                </imageobject>
                                        </mediaobject>
                                </figure>
                        </para>
                        <para>图中，操作系统安装完成，系统自动重启，输入用户名和密码进入系统</para>
                        <para>
                                <figure id="eayunos-install-eayunos-manager-6"><title>图7</title>
                                    <mediaobject>
                                        <imageobject>
                                            <imagedata fileref="images/eayunos-manager-7.png" format="PNG" scale="100"/>
                                        </imageobject>
                                    </mediaobject>
                                </figure>
